title: Day 852
content:
# Day 852

Today was one of those nights (what a way to start a sentence lol) where I lay down, plan to get up, then fall asleep. Naturally my body knows when a Medium is due so it wakes me up and I come out here to write. However, I'm ready to go back to bed.

Thank you body for the reminder; the streak lives on!

7/21/24

Conor Jay Chepenik
